37void md5_block_data_order(MD5_CTX *c, const void *data_, size_t num)
38{
39 const unsigned char *data = data_;
40 register MD32_REG_T A, B, C, D, l;
41# ifndef MD32_XARRAY
42 /* See comment in crypto/sha/sha_locl.h for details. */
43 MD32_REG_T XX0, XX1, XX2, XX3, XX4, XX5, XX6, XX7,
44 XX8, XX9, XX10, XX11, XX12, XX13, XX14, XX15;
45# define X(i) XX##i
46# else

48# define X(i) XX[i]

51 A = c->A;
52 B = c->B;

63 (void)HOST_c2l(data, l);
